  "text": "Teleport has encountered an error when its target is empty.\n\n### Vue version\n\nlatest\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nclick the button\n\n### What is expected?\n\nThe browser does not display any errors.\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nThe browser has encountered an error.\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
